Cell["\<\
Consider a qubit in a pure state. This time, the quantum state is expressed \
in terns of the computational basis state.\
\>", "ExampleText",
 CellID->1750296343,ExpressionUUID->"abead18a-86c0-4e4e-b4d5-08cea55d140b"],

